# Site shell (wide — 1920px max)

Page content is capped at **1920px** (`--site-max-width`), centered with `margin-inline: auto`.

- `html` background: **#FCF9F9** (or **#000** on `page-dark`) — visible as **equal side gutters** when viewport > 1920px
- `body`: `width: min(100%, 1920px)`, centered
- `.nav-wrapper`: `max-width: 1920px`, `left: 50%`, `translateX(-50%)`

**full-width** (`layout--full`) = 100% of the shell, not `100vw`.

**narrow** (`layout--narrow`) — see `layout-width.mdc`.
